{
  "texts": [
    "In the realm of health, AI significantly contributes to nutritional analysis and personalized dietary recommendations.",
    "By analyzing individual dietary patterns and preferences, AI algorithms craft meal plans tailored to health objectives while prioritizing taste satisfaction.",
    "Personalized nutrition platforms leverage machine learning to provide dynamic feedback and adjustments, helping individuals maintain balanced diets that align with their unique health needs (Wang et al. 2024).",
    "These platforms can track users' dietary habits and suggest modifications based on real-time data, thus promoting healthier eating behaviors.",
    "Moreover, AI has been leveraged to address specific dietary conditions."
  ]
}